headline: Infleqtion Appoints J. Eric Bjornholt to its Board of Directors
summary: BOULDER, Colo., January 27, 2026--Infleqtion, a global leader in quantum sensing and quantum computing powered by neutral-atom technology, announced the appointment of J. Eric Bjornholt to its Board of Directors effective immediately.
